Arsitektur Chroma:
Open WebUI
    ↓
ChromaDB Server
    ↓
Chroma UI

Chroma disarankan:
ChromaDB server : chromadb/chroma
Chroma UI       : chromadb-admin

Install:
1. Buat Docker network bersama
docker network create rag-network
docker network connect rag-network ollama
docker network connect rag-network open-webui

2. Jalankan ChromaDB server
mkdir -p ~/chroma-data
docker run -d \
  --name chromadb \
  --restart unless-stopped \
  --network rag-network \
  -p 8000:8000 \
  -v ~/chroma-data:/data \
  chromadb/chroma:latest
cek: docker ps
uji: curl http://localhost:8000/api/v2/heartbeat

3. Bangun chromadb-admin langsung dari source
sudo apt update
sudo apt install -y git

Clone Proyek:
cd ~
git clone https://github.com/flanker/chromadb-admin.git
cd chromadb-admin

Build image lokal:
docker build -t chromadb-admin-local .

Kemudian jalankan:
docker run -d \
  --name chromadb-admin \
  --restart unless-stopped \
  --network rag-network \
  -p 3001:3001 \
  chromadb-admin-local

Periksa:
docker ps

Buka:
http://localhost:3001

4. Alamat ChromaDB pada UI
masukkan:
Chroma URL : http://chromadb:8000
Tenant     : default_tenant
Database   : default_database
http://ollama:11434/v1/embeddings
nomic-embed-text:latest

5. Sambungkan Open WebUI
catat volume
open-webui  ->  /app/backend/data

Buat ulang Open WebUI dengan koneksi Chroma eksternal
docker stop open-webui
docker rm open-webui
docker run -d \
  --name open-webui \
  --restart unless-stopped \
  --network rag-network \
  -p 3000:8080 \
  -e OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://ollama:11434 \
  -e VECTOR_DB=chroma \
  -e CHROMA_HTTP_HOST=chromadb \
  -e CHROMA_HTTP_PORT=8000 \
  -e CHROMA_TENANT=default_tenant \
  -e CHROMA_DATABASE=default_database \
  -v open-webui:/app/backend/data \
  ghcr.io/open-webui/open-webui:main

Verifikasi konfigurasi
docker inspect open-webui \
  --format '{{range .Config.Env}}{{println .}}{{end}}' \
  | grep -E 'VECTOR_DB|CHROMA_HTTP'

docker exec open-webui \
  curl http://chromadb:8000/api/v2/heartbeat

6. Reindex Knowledge Base
Buka Open WebUI:
http://localhost:3000
Kemudian:
Admin Panel
→ Settings
→ Documents
→ Reindex Knowledge Base
Atau unggah satu dokumen baru ke Knowledge sebagai pengujian.

7. Muat ulang Chroma Admin
Setelah reindex selesai, buka kembali:
http://localhost:3001
Lalu refresh halaman.
